# 14. TESTING AND VALIDATION
# ============================================================================

## 14.1 Unit Testing
- Test each module independently
- Use synthetic IQ data for testing
- Test edge cases (low SNR, high CFO, etc.)
- Validate against known signals

## 14.2 Integration Testing
- Test module-to-module data flow
- Verify thread safety under load
- Test with real HackRF hardware
- Measure end-to-end latency

## 14.3 Performance Benchmarks
Target processing times:
- CFO correction: <1 ms (1024 samples)
- DSP measurements: <2 ms
- AI inference: <50 ms (CPU), <5 ms (GPU)
